column5: Hi all,  Still a good 18" of ice here, but I think it's going to go fast now. Got out with my best friend and fishing buddy Roloff the other evening for a couple of hours, nice to have the pup along now its warming up.  Got some walleye and a few pike to bite, great way to spend an evening.
Another great video, thanks for sharing. PS I hate you LOL
HMMMMMMMMMMM Still no white fish fest. WTH. LOL

Nice going Simon!!!!  Thanks man!    Another great video, thanks for sharing. PS I hate you LOL  LOL...really....hate is such a strong word, maybe I just annoy you a little.....lol.   HMMMMMMMMMMM Still no white fish fest. WTH. LOL   Ah man, don't think its gonna happen this year, ice is pretty sketchy now, last time I went to my whitefish lake there was a pressure crack running shore to shore, had to cross it, there was open water there a week ago, no way Im venturing out there now.
